Our
Privacy Notice for California Consumers supplements the information
contained in our Privacy Policy and applies solely to visitors,
users, and others who reside in the State of California (“Consumers”,
“You”). We adopt this notice to comply with the
California Consumer Privacy Act of 2018 (“CCPA”) and
other California privacy laws.
We
do not sell Your Personal Information to anyone
or share it with third parties for their own marketing purposes.
